A teleport destination, or derived actor, is where actors are moved by the [[:Category:Teleport specials|Teleport line specials]]. This destination can be given a height (Z) value and be used to teleport over a pit for a trap, a [[3D floor]], a [[Classes:Bridge|bridge thing]] or similar solid obstacle.


